[2026-06-18T02:19:12.891Z] [TOOL_RESULT] {"id":"call_00_tNAdDOnL3iQJreJAxhk22566","name":"read_file","elapsed_ms":9,"ok":true,"output":"import tkinter as tk\r\nfrom tkinter import ttk, filedialog, messagebox, scrolledtext\r\nimport threading\r\nimport os\r\nimport json\r\nimport re\r\n\r\n# ─── CONFIG FILE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\nCONFIG_FILE = \"reup_config.json\"\r\n\r\ndef load_config():\r\n    if os.path.exists(CONFIG_FILE):\r\n        with open(CONFIG_FILE, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\r\n            return json.load(f)\r\n    return {}\r\n\r\ndef save_config(cfg):\r\n    with open(CONFIG_FILE, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\r\n        json.dump(cfg, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\r\n\r\n# ─── COLORS & FONTS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\nBG        = \"#0f0f13\"\r\nPANEL     = \"#1a1a22\"\r\nCARD      = \"#22222e\"\r\nACCENT    = \"#7c5cfc\"\r\nACCENT2   = \"#a78bfa\"\r\nGREEN     = \"#22c55e\"\r\nRED       = \"#ef4444\"\r\nYELLOW    = \"#f59e0b\"\r\nTEXT      = \"#e2e8f0\"\r\nSUBTEXT   = \"#94a3b8\"\r\nBORDER    = \"#2e2e3e\"\r\n\r\nFONT_SM   = (\"Segoe UI\", 8)\r\nFONT_BASE = (\"Segoe UI\", 9)\r\nFONT_MED  = (\"Segoe UI\", 10, \"bold\")\r\nFONT_LG   = (\"Segoe UI\", 12, \"bold\")\r\nFONT_XL   = (\"Segoe UI\", 14, \"bold\")\r\n\r\nVOICES = [\r\n    \"vi-VN-HoaiMyNeural\",\r\n    \"vi-VN-NamMinhNeural\",\r\n    \"en-US-JennyNeural\",\r\n    \"en-US-GuyNeural\",\r\n    \"en-GB-SoniaNeural\",\r\n    \"ja-JP-NanamiNeural\",\r\n    \"zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural\",\r\n    \"ko-KR-SunHiNeural\",\r\n    \"fr-FR-DeniseNeural\",\r\n    \"de-DE-KatjaNeural\",\r\n]\r\n\r\nTTS_ENGINES = [\"Edge TTS (Miễn phí)\", \"Google TTS\", \"ElevenLabs API\", \"OpenAI TTS\"]\r\n\r\n# ─── TOOLTIP ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\nclass ToolTip:\r\n    def __init__(self, widget, text):\r\n        self.widget = widget\r\n        self.text = text\r\n        widget.bind(\"<Enter>\", self.show)\r\n        widget.bind(\"<Leave>\", self.hide)\r\n        self.tw = None\r\n\r\n    def show(self, event=None):\r\n        x = self.widget.winfo_rootx() + 20\r\n        y = self.widget.winfo_rooty() + self.widget.winfo_height() + 4\r\n        self.tw = tw = tk.Toplevel(self.widget)\r\n        tw.wm_overrideredirect(True)\r\n        tw.wm_geome"}
[2026-06-18T02:19:12.892Z] [TOOL_RESULT] {"id":"call_01_Xwn1B3yMcfEttHKLcorp3845","name":"read_file","elapsed_ms":9,"ok":true,"output":"---\r\ndescription: Reup-video execution guardrail\r\nglobs:\r\n  - \"**/*\"\r\nalwaysApply: true\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Reup Video Rule\r\n\r\nBefore making substantial changes in this repository:\r\n\r\n1. Read `AGENTS.md` for product constraints, legal/policy context, and engineering guardrails.\r\n2. Read `PROJECT_PLAN.md` and align work to `Current_focus`.\r\n3. Implement only the highest-priority in-progress item unless the user explicitly reprioritizes.\r\n4. After each meaningful milestone, update `PROJECT_PLAN.md`:\r\n   - move task status (`todo`/`doing`/`done`)\r\n   - append a short line in `Changelog`\r\n   - refresh `Current_focus` for the next agent session\r\n5. Do not introduce automation intended to bypass platform ToS. Prefer official APIs or human-in-the-loop publish flow.\r\n6. Architecture is **Laravel (orchestrator) + separate local worker repo** for ML/ffmpeg. Heavy processing belongs in the worker; Laravel coordinates and persists state. If a change touches the Laravel–worker contract, update **both** sides and document it in `PROJECT_PLAN.md` / changelog.\r\n"}
[2026-06-18T02:19:12.892Z] [TOOL_RESULT] {"id":"call_02_k86DabGJRsgV1caSsd9l9496","name":"read_file","elapsed_ms":8,"ok":true,"output":"# reup-video\r\n\r\nMonorepo: **Laravel** (orchestrator) + **worker** (ASR/TTS/ffmpeg) + **contract** (HTTP API v1).\r\n\r\nSee [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) and [PROJECT_PLAN.md](PROJECT_PLAN.md).\r\n\r\n## Phase 0 — ingest (Douyin-first)\r\n\r\n1. Install yt-dlp: `pip install yt-dlp` (Windows: binary is often in `%APPDATA%\\Python\\Python311\\Scripts\\yt-dlp.exe` — add to PATH or leave `YTDLP_PATH=yt-dlp` for auto-detect).\r\n2. Douyin: `jingxuan?modal_id=…` links are auto-converted to `https://www.douyin.com/video/{id}`. Downloads still need `YTDLP_COOKIES_FILE` (exported `cookies.txt` from a logged-in browser session).\r\n\r\n```bash\r\ncd laravel\r\ncp .env.example .env\r\nphp artisan migrate\r\nphp artisan video:download \"https://www.douyin.com/video/...\"\r\nphp artisan video:process --source-video=1\r\n```\r\n\r\nWorker must be running (`worker/README.md`). `video:process` still accepts a local file path without `--source-video`.\r\n\r\n## Layout (private storage)\r\n\r\n```\r\nlaravel/storage/app/private/\r\n  sources/{Y}/{m}/{id}/original.mp4\r\n  out/{job_id}.mp4\r\n  processed/   # reserved\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Tests\r\n\r\n```bash\r\ncd laravel && php artisan test\r\ncd worker && pytest\r\n```\r\n"}
