me machine should use the same base (e.g. `storage/app/...`).\r\n\r\n## Source ingest (Phase 0, Laravel only)\r\n\r\nDownloading from a source URL (Douyin-first via `yt-dlp`) is **not** part of this HTTP contract. Laravel persists `source_videos` a"}
